burlap.oomdp.stochasticgames.tournament.common

Class ConstantWorldGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.oomdp.stochasticgames.tournament.common.ConstantWorldGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WorldGenerator

    public class ConstantWorldGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
implements WorldGenerator
    A WorldGenerator that always generators the same WorldConfiguraiton. It takes the same parameters as a World constructor and simply passes them to the World Constructor when a new World needs to be generated.
    Author:
    James MacGlashan

        sg - a state generator for generating initial states of a game
